dividends on our common stock in the future will be at the discretion of our board of", "bbox": [162.5, 1059.1, 1052.7, 1079.9]}, {"text": "directors and will depend upon our results of operations, earnings, capital requirements, financial condition,", "bbox": [162.5, 1084.1, 1062.8, 1104.9]}, {"text": "future prospects, contractual restrictions, and other factors deemed relevant by our board of directors. TD Group", "bbox": [162.5, 1109.1, 1100.4, 1129.9]}, {"text": "is a holding company and conducts all of its operations through direct and indirect subsidiaries. Unless TD Group", "bbox": [162.5, 1134.1, 1111.9, 1154.9]}, {"text": "receives dividends, distributions, advances, transfers of funds or other payments from our subsidiaries, TD Group", "bbox": [162.5, 1159.1, 1110.8, 1179.9]}, {"text": "will be unable to pay any dividends on our common stock in the future. The ability of any subsidiaries to take", "bbox": [162.5, 1184.1, 1077.6, 1204.9]}, {"text": "any of the foregoing actions is limited by the terms of our debt documents and may be limited by future debt or", "bbox": [162.5, 1209.1, 1091.8, 1229.9]}, {"text": "other agreements that we may enter into.", "bbox": [162.5, 1234.1, 502.7, 1254.9]}, {"text": "18", "bbox": [627.1, 1484.1, 647.9, 1504.9]}]}